setBtechopen(!Btechopen)}> Btech {!Btechopen ? : }
setMtechopen(!Mtechopen)}> Mtech {!Mtechopen ? : }
setPhdopen(!Phdopen)}> Phd {!Phdopen ? : }
) } export default Programme
